Built a custom GPT to answer all your music law questions - can also analyze and draft simple agreements and do royalty calculations! This is trained on some of the best, most up to date music law texts.

Posting here for anyone who wants to try it out (it’s free!) please try and stump it or break it, provide feedback so we can keep training it up!

Can do small agreements, royalty calculations, and answer anything (I think!) in the music law world. 

Been getting some good feedback today from label ppl and some fellow writers. Updating the model to suit. 

Link in bio or just copy/paste

https://chat.openai.com/g/g-l1vlXrT4d-music-law-maven

This is maybe the best melody assistant we can get!
